UseGPUReduction no
Useflag yes

NumberOfInitializationCycles 10000
NumberOfEquilibrationCycles  0
NumberOfProductionCycles     10000

UseMaxStep  yes
MaxStepPerCycle 1

UseChargesFromCIFFile yes

RestartFile no
RandomSeed  0

BMCBiasingMethod LJ_Biasing

NumberOfTrialPositions 10
NumberOfTrialOrientations 10
NumberOfBlocks 1
AdsorbateAllocateSpace 10240
NumberOfSimulations 1
SingleSimulation yes

DifferentFrameworks yes
InputFileType cif
FrameworkName NaX_Al55
UnitCells 0 1 1 1

ChargeMethod Ewald
Temperature 303
Pressure    10000

OverlapCriteria 1e5
CutOffVDW 12.0
CutOffCoulomb 12.0
EwaldPrecision 1e-6

SeparateFrameworkComponents yes
NumberofFrameworkComponents 2
UseChargesFromCIFFile         yes
Framework_Component_ 1
TranslationProbability     1.0
END_OF_Framework_Component_ 1

UseDNNforHostGuest no

Component 0 MoleculeName             CO2
            IdealGasRosenbluthWeight 1.0
            FugacityCoefficient      PR-EOS
            BlockPockets             yes
            BlockPocketsFilename     FAU
            TranslationProbability   1.0
            RotationProbability      1.0
            ReinsertionProbability   1.0
            SwapProbability          1.0
            CreateNumberOfMolecules  0
